{"data":[{"id":562806887,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"276fa0bc5305193ab096781d0e4844ef","url_token":"luo-da-you-99","name":"尽黑丶","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7739b5ebd3ed72ce997d2557d1e494ea_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7739b5ebd3ed72ce997d2557d1e494ea_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/276fa0bc5305193ab096781d0e4844ef","user_type":"people","headline":"自闭","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":486,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562806887","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546148377,"updated_time":1546279472,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":19,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我高估他的数理逻辑水平了，首先举出两个逻辑错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果定义了A为满足性质B的数，那么对于数a，你不能假设a满足非B以反证关于A的命题成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这句话可以有更简单的表述，也即，一个错误的前提可以推出任何结论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e假设不考虑错误1（1成立）那么\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（2）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你不能举出存在一个负质数反例就认为分解P的组合存在，换句话说，你最多只证明了2=-1+3，那么对于26=6k+2=-1+27，你这个分解不成立的时候，你又过来和我说27=6k+3是合数，可是6k+3是合数跟其他组合成不成立有什么关系呢？实际上你并没有说明26=19+7的原因\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有人说他只证明了偶数可以分解成两个奇数，我觉得他的证明好像还不够强，其实只说明了，一个奇合数可以被分解为一个偶数和一个奇数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后的最后，还是想说一句话，\u003cb\u003e天才永远相信他所说的话对全人类而言的正确，亦永远相信这句话对于真理而言的错误\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回首历史的长河，那些人类的群星，从亚里士多德，哥白尼，牛顿，麦克斯韦到爱因斯坦，他们只是修正了一些微小的理论。就算是天才，也要明白，真理无穷，最聪明的人穷尽一生的智慧，也不过贡献为全人类前进一寸的微弱力量。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许题主以后会有更大的成就，然而，一个能改变世界的人，一定是先认识自己的人，共勉！\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我高估他的数理逻辑水平了，首先举出两个逻辑错误。（1）如果定义了A为满足性质B的数，那么对于数a，你不能假设a满足非B以反证关于A的命题成立 这句话可以有更简单的表述，也即，一个错误的前提可以推出任何结论。 假设不考虑错误1（1成立）那么（2）你不能…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=197\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_e